            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef is cooking, heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion petals </strong>and <strong>pepper strips </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
