    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>red chilli relish</strong>, <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>chilli sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
