      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>crispy beef</strong> and <strong>chilli sauce</strong> to the pan and stir it all together</p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>crispy chilli beef</strong></p>",
